094", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75458102_1450189572293427_321153024598500436_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=QRC9yR9WiIcQ7kNvgFA2NwG&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCVTB_b-PMdgzTzIwXBWuyH1p1PexSNbHB2UiF1GJfNEg&oe=670136FB"}, "display_name": "Strike Master", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Strike Master: The Ultimate VR Bowling Experience\n\nWelcome to \"Strike Master,\" where the classic sport of bowling transcends the ordinary and enters a realm of immersive virtual reality. Get ready to embark on a cosmic adventure that transforms traditional bowling into an exhilarating and futuristic experience. Whether you're a seasoned bowler or new to the game, \"Strike Master\" offers a fresh and captivating way to enjoy this beloved sport.\nGame Overview\n\n\"Strike Master\" is a cutting-edge VR game that redefines the bowling experience by placing players in a vibrant cosmic arena. The game challenges your precision, skill, and timing as you aim to score points by knocking down pins in various celestial-themed lanes. Each game session offers a unique adventure, filled with stunning visuals and dynamic gameplay.", "short_description": "Strike Master: The Ultimate VR Bowling Experience\n\nWelcome to \"Strike Master,\" where the classic sport of bowling transcends the ordinary and enters a realm of immersive virtual reality. Get ready to embark on a cosmic adventure that transforms traditional bowling into an exhilarating and futuristic experience. Whether you're a seasoned bowler or new to the game, \"Strike Master\" offers a fresh and captivating way to enjoy this beloved sport."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/strike-master-vr/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "LC Invention", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/strike-master-vr", "category": null, "comfort_rating": nul